{"tid":1626840,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"【粵語】1987：逆權公民","createTime":"2019-10-05T13:14:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T14:06:56.000Z","uid":69384,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7a7b70e3081f782e95941828189c39567f3ca6af","tid":1626840,"uid":69384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:14:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/WkKYtkM/0-2e-D5-DNM1w-CUq-AHLg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2FWkKYtkM%2F0-2e-D5-DNM1w-CUq-AHLg.jpg&h=2906503f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>主台:</strong><a href=\"http://sk-knower.com/user/chicktv?live=okru\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fchicktv%3Flive%3Dokru&d=YADvn44w83N9IBOkVydrk%2FaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=395bad98\" target=\"_blank\">http://sk-knower.com/user/chicktv?live=okru</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">專頁:</span></strong><a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/nikuniku\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fnikuniku&d=YADvn44w83N9IBOkVydrk%2FaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=bfa0ea6f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/nikuniku</a>"},{"pid":"2f78a39a730f0454c97aabc43bd243271706ae08","tid":1626840,"uid":69384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:15:57.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"03853c5abc47e5b794457bce7fa1a242224db450","tid":1626840,"uid":295981,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:16:26.000Z","msg":"一係唔㩒錢，一㩒就㩒盡佢！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1626821\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1626821</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n推"},{"pid":"a4a5de6f3d37486fa37dd9195fa801cc551922c1","tid":1626840,"uid":69384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:17:52.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"6c172042954095a7c25bfe015a39dbb504442a5c","tid":1626840,"uid":69384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:22:59.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"37da9d688e715671321061b1731422f992cf1f59","tid":1626840,"uid":69384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:26:07.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"f0abe714756ee6935738d4fe7fccbefbac564930","tid":1626840,"uid":69384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:34:18.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"e8fe4bceb614d0bc51ae903413d54b249349dc8f","tid":1626840,"uid":261478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:34:47.000Z","msg":"聽曰港島記住係和平遊行<br />\n盡量吸多D和理非出黎<br />\n和理非唔好怕無不反對通知書<br />\n香港已經唔講法律<br />\n有不反對通知書都照拉鳩你架啦<br />\n所以聽日為香港全世界出黎港島<br />\n勇和一家目標300萬人和平遊行<br />\n畀人知道香港人係和平嘅<br />\n暴力嘅係政府<br />\n要吸多D國際支持<br />\n<br />\n同時我唔反對衝衝子去衝<br />\n但記住要散水返左屋企先<br />\n避免畀狗圍無路走唔到<br />\n返左屋企之後再係屋企步行範圍內快閃游擊<br />\n拆鐵拆政府建築幫中資國企裝修<br />\n裝修到星期二開唔到門就變相三罷<br />\n唔好等有狗出現就要散水轉場<br />\n記住我地優勢係人多機動性高<br />\n攰同餓就返屋企食飯休息回滿升先再第日出過<br />\n有唔對路就返屋企訓覺唔好送頭<br />\n<br />\n幫手推POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1626523/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1626523/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"a7c64a5489e31064abf3dfdd2d5eada6ba664b56","tid":1626840,"uid":69384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:37:40.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"b3002062c274176cb6e48cf61abf261cc13639ca","tid":1626840,"uid":69384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:46:02.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"c875a49de161037827e598d35f760989beae703a","tid":1626840,"uid":69384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:53:22.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"ffbc7d2fe9b5a1420b08fd314b9227f2a80019fb","tid":1626840,"uid":69384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:57:54.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"074fa32c0e5877ca85ddf68ed72cd7a5e57e4727","tid":1626840,"uid":69384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T14:01:04.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"38c912c2b11ad2ccf564c82cf9cc5240adf6a83f","tid"